title: Desktop vacuum packaging machine US-DZ-260C
short_description: Another small vacuum packaging equipment is the US-DZ-260C model. The equipment operates at a voltage of 220V, has a power of 0.26 kW, the size of the vacuum chamber is 330*270*50 mm, the length of the packaged package is 255 mm, the hot-gluing area is 8 mm, the total weight of the equipment is 20 kg. Dimensions: length 410 mm, width 320 mm and height 320 mm.
short_description_uz: Kichik vakumli qadoqlash uskunalaridan yana biri US-DZ-260C modelidir. Uskuna 220V kuchlanishda ishlaydi, 0.26 kW quvvatga ega, vakumlash kamerasi o'lchami 330*270*50 mm, qadoqlanadigan paket uzunligi 255 mm, qizdirib yopishtiriladigan joyi 8 mm, uskunaning umumiy vazni 20 kg ni tashkil qiladi. O'lchamlari: uzunligi 410 mm, kengligi 320 mm va balandligi 320 mm.
